data.description:
"Welcome to this charming home nestled in the heart of Weatherford! Step inside and discover a wealth of desirable features awaiting you. From the expansive backyard, perfect for entertaining, to the abundant natural light flooding through the windows, this home offers a delightful living experience.

The seamless flow from the living room to the kitchen and dining area makes hosting gatherings a breeze. Culinary enthusiasts will appreciate the ample cabinet space in the kitchen, while the spacious master bedroom boasts a walk-in closet designed to accommodate even the most extensive wardrobes.

Enjoy the luxurious feel of the wood LTV floors underfoot and the convenience of a generously sized laundry room for all your daily chores. With a large 2-car garage capable of accommodating even oversized vehicles, this home is truly designed with convenience in mind. There is a large shop in the back yard to keep everything from your lawn mower to all your gardening tools. Also, the house is getting a brand-new breaker panel. 

Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this your dream home! Schedule your appointment today and experience the countless treasures this property has to offer."
